<li><strong><span class="mx-px mb-1 inline-block rounded-md bg-secondary px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs leading-normal">src/pages/Manager.tsx</span></strong><span> — Completely different manager dashboard: pie chart, bar chart, map, approve/reject controls, CSV export</span></li>
